OL,3,CCommunities Secretary 'appalled' by
OL,4,CMuslim charity run excluding women
OL,6,FThe Communities Secretary said he was
OL,7,F"horrified" and "appalled" by a Muslim
OL,8,Fcharity run in a London park which
OL,9,Fexcluded women from participating.
OL,11,FEast London Mosque, which organised
OL,12,FSunday's run in Victoria Park
OL,13,Falongside the London Muslim Centre,
OL,14,Fsaid hundreds of runners and
OL,15,Fsupporters had gathered for the
OL,16,Fcommunity event.
