OL,3,CCommunities Secretary 'appalled' by
OL,4,CMuslim charity run excluding women
OL,6,FBilled on the Muslim Charity Run
OL,7,Fwebsite as an "inclusive 5km race"
OL,8,Fwelcoming "runners and supporters of
OL,9,Fall ages and abilities", the event was
OL,10,Fopen to "men, boys of all ages and
OL,11,Fgirls under 12".
OL,13,FCommunities Secretary Steve Reed
OL,14,Fdescribed it as "absolutely
OL,15,Funacceptable" for women to be
OL,16,F"blocked" from participating and said
OL,17,Fthe Equality and Human Rights
OL,18,FCommission (EHRC) will determine
OL,19,Fwhether any laws or regulations have
OL,20,Fbeen breached.
