OL,3,CCommunities Secretary 'appalled' by
OL,4,CMuslim charity run excluding women
OL,6,FMr Reed told LBC Radio: "I saw these
OL,7,Freports... and I was as horrified as
OL,8,Fanybody else.
OL,10,F"It's absolutely unacceptable that
OL,11,Fwomen should be blocked from going on
OL,12,Fa fun run in a public space when the
OL,13,Fmen are allowed to go out there and do
OL,14,Fthat.
OL,16,F"Now we have an equalities watchdog,
OL,17,FI'm sure that they will be aware of
OL,18,Fthis case.
OL,26,@nD@YOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
