OL,3,CCommunities Secretary 'appalled' by
OL,4,CMuslim charity run excluding women
OL,6,F"It's getting a lot of publicity, and
OL,7,Fquite rightly so, and they will
OL,8,Fdetermine whether there has been any
OL,9,Fbreach of the law or regulations and
OL,10,Fthen I'm sure sanctions will follow as
OL,11,Fappropriate.
OL,13,F"But speaking for myself, I was
OL,14,Fappalled."
OL,16,FHe added: "We do not want a situation
OL,17,Fin this country where men are allowed
OL,18,Fto do things that women are then
OL,19,Fbarred from. We cannot tolerate that."
