OL,3,CCommunities Secretary 'appalled' by
OL,4,CMuslim charity run excluding women
OL,6,FHe said: "Well done to each and every
OL,7,Fone of you, especially to the
OL,8,Fyoungsters and the elders and the
OL,9,Fcommunity at large for participating
OL,10,Ftoday."
OL,12,FThe council said it has contacted the
OL,13,Fmosque to "seek urgent clarification"
OL,14,Fafter "reports about age and gender
OL,15,Frestrictions".
OL,17,FThe EHRC is understood to be looking
OL,18,Finto the matter following a report by
OL,19,Fthe Mail on Sunday.
