OL,3,CCommunities Secretary 'appalled' by
OL,4,CMuslim charity run excluding women
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the commission
OL,7,Fsaid: "The EHRC receives complaints
OL,8,Feach week about allegations of
OL,9,Funlawful activity contrary to the
OL,10,FEquality Act 2010. We consider each
OL,11,Fcomplaint carefully and take action
OL,12,Fwhere appropriate."
OL,14,FCertain exceptions under equality law
OL,15,Fcan apply to charities and religion or
OL,16,Fbelief organisations, including
OL,17,Fpotentially restricting events to one
OL,18,Fsex only.
