OL,6,FA Tower Hamlets Council spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was an independent event
OL,8,Fheld in Victoria Park, not organised
OL,9,Fby the council.
OL,11,F"Like many local charitable events, it
OL,12,Fmade use of the park space.
OL,14,F"Following the reports about age and
OL,15,Fgender restrictions, the council has
OL,16,Fcontacted East London Mosque to seek
OL,17,Furgent clarification.
